  "title": "Manufacturing Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Work Location:</strong><br />Gul (company transport provided from Boon Lay MRT)</p><p><strong>Salary Range:</strong><br />$1,900 – $2,200 (commensurate with experience)</p><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong><br />Monday to Friday<br />9:00 AM – 5:30 PM<br />(No shift work)</p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Handle filling and packing of chemical products into drums and bottles according to standard operating procedures</p></li><li><p>Perform visual checks to ensure proper sealing, labeling, and packaging quality</p></li><li><p>Assist in basic housekeeping to maintain a clean and safe work environment</p></li><li><p>Follow workplace safety guidelines and instructions at all times</p></li><li><p>Carry out other ad-hoc duties as assigned by the supervisor</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum NITEC qualification or equivalent</p></li><li><p>Able to handle physical work, including lifting loads of approximately 5–10 kg</p></li><li><p>Comfortable working in a manufacturing/production environment</p></li><li><p>Able to commence work at short notice<br /></p><p>Loh Chiang Soon (CEI No. R1873093)</p><p>Business Edge Personnel Services Pte Ltd (96C4864)</p></li></ul>",
